short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: TechPro Hosted Phone System clients can use Call_Click to call numbers on web page from their desk phone.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Note, users must be registered with TechPro's Call Client to use this extension. Users are required to log in with their Call Client credentials and on the appropriate PBX server. Once logged in, clicking on a phone number will activate it. Click a 2nd time to initiate a call from your desk phone to that number.
